  <name>Pomodorot</name>
  <summary>A pomodoro timer which can block your screen during breaks</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Pomodorot is a timer app which can be used to set 20 minute breaks where you move for 20 seconds for blood circulation or also can be used as a pomodoro timer. Its main difference being the ability to block the screen when its break time so that you don't ignore it impulsively.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Variable time options</li>
      <li>Minimal</li>
      <li>Easy on the eyes</li>
      <li>Command line startup (can be used as an autostart with --start-timer arg)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
